{"tid":707710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔LULU 18世界盃波衫POST全紀錄","createTime":"2018-06-18T22:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T00:09:50.000Z","uid":64156,"like":27,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"af70eec41d861c1390d6bed05ee3fc6349c42145","tid":707710,"uid":64156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T22:23:48.000Z","msg":"今屆2018世界盃<br />\n大埔Lulu開著波衫post + 開名讚彈相應球員全紀錄<br />\n<br />\n1）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/061109_a363050b8f9d6e4763c7752b43b00b78.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F061109_a363050b8f9d6e4763c7752b43b00b78.png&h=0799e16c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估俄羅斯小勝<br />\n點名讚迪沙哥夫<br />\n點名擔心38歲老將伊拿舒域<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果俄羅斯大勝5比0<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迪沙哥夫20分鐘拉親傷出 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伊拿舒域踢足全場表現出色<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/061128_d6970093d717c980e69eac5e38181fae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F061128_d6970093d717c980e69eac5e38181fae.png&h=303d2a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估西班牙贏2:0<br />\n點名讚迪基亞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果西班牙3比3和葡萄牙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迪基亞罕有地派大膠 （呢個最堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n3）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/061150_b9cb2d307976d23067b4ab9c49d996f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F061150_b9cb2d307976d23067b4ab9c49d996f7.png&h=af0b7f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估德國大勝<br />\n點名話德國對手墨西哥龍門奧祖亞幾勁都難以不失球<br />\n點名讚奧斯爾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果德國0比1負墨西哥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奧祖亞表現出色 不失一球<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奧斯爾隱形全場<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/061213_693bb52b47de13e79e3f9628395bc4e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F061213_693bb52b47de13e79e3f9628395bc4e8.png&h=a2708110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔駛多講<br />\n實實際際<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lulutung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flulutung%2F&d=vqM4mCGDxYbl5X62wekB3hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4580d482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lulutung/</a><br />\n要買波等下一個波衫post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween 有冇巴打有蕭生同沈大師今屆嘅紀錄參考參考？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82379deffca9b6ffff70f9aa92e5c151a74677ca","tid":707710,"uid":184391,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T23:1